Features:
• Generate QR code with one click: Easily convert the current webpage URL into a QR code;
• Customize QR code content: Modify the URL content in the input box, and the QR code will be automatically updated;
• Safer: You can actively delete private content in the URL, such as token, session, etc., to avoid privacy leakage;
• Simple operation: Easy to use, no technical foundation is required, even novices can easily get started.

Instructions:
1. After installing the plug-in, click the plug-in icon on the browser toolbar, and the QR code of the current webpage URL will be displayed by default.
3. Modify the URL content in the input box, and the QR code will be automatically updated.
